<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: psychic soothe -->
  <PsychicDroneCultist.stages.psychic_soothe.label>心灵抚慰</PsychicDroneCultist.stages.psychic_soothe.label>
  <!-- EN: It's like a calming voice at the back of my mind, soothing me, settling my nerves. -->
  <PsychicDroneCultist.stages.psychic_soothe.description>一种使人平静的声音在我脑内回荡，抚慰着我，让我感到十分放松。</PsychicDroneCultist.stages.psychic_soothe.description>
  <!-- EN: low psychic drone -->
  <PsychicDroneCultist.stages.low_psychic_drone.label>心灵低语（低）</PsychicDroneCultist.stages.low_psychic_drone.label>
  <!-- EN: It's like a scratching at the back of my mind. A voice, whispering. I can only make out a few words, and I recognize the song calling to me. -->
  <PsychicDroneCultist.stages.low_psychic_drone.description>似乎有什么东西正在侵扰我的思想，一种声音，一种在我耳边低语的声音，我只能听清几个字，唯一能确定的就是这个声音在不停的呼喊我。</PsychicDroneCultist.stages.low_psychic_drone.description>
  <!-- EN: moderate psychic drone -->
  <PsychicDroneCultist.stages.moderate_psychic_drone.label>心灵低语（中）</PsychicDroneCultist.stages.moderate_psychic_drone.label>
  <!-- EN: I feel like the voice could be coming from just around the corner. -->
  <PsychicDroneCultist.stages.moderate_psychic_drone.description>我感觉周围总是有看不见的人在跟我说话，声音一直在变但是内容不变，说我应该去伤害他人，快让它消失吧！</PsychicDroneCultist.stages.moderate_psychic_drone.description>
  <!-- EN: high psychic drone -->
  <PsychicDroneCultist.stages.high_psychic_drone.label>心灵低语（高）</PsychicDroneCultist.stages.high_psychic_drone.label>
  <!-- EN: The voice is serene and comforting -->
  <PsychicDroneCultist.stages.high_psychic_drone.description>说话的声音太响了，难以承受，精神也无法集中，我试图跟它说话，对着它吼叫，但是都毫无效果！</PsychicDroneCultist.stages.high_psychic_drone.description>
  <!-- EN: extreme psychic drone -->
  <PsychicDroneCultist.stages.extreme_psychic_drone.label>心灵低语（极高）</PsychicDroneCultist.stages.extreme_psychic_drone.label>
  <!-- EN: My heart pounds and I'm sweating. The call has found me. -->
  <PsychicDroneCultist.stages.extreme_psychic_drone.description>我的心脏在疯狂跳动，我浑身上下都是汗，我现在只想杀掉我周围的这些敌人，他们是我的噩梦……噩梦……噩梦……</PsychicDroneCultist.stages.extreme_psychic_drone.description>
  
</LanguageData>